@startuml
title SE Owner QuanLyAudioMapLink
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
actor "Chủ quán" as O
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/WEB/app.js function renderAudioSources()" as RENDER
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/WEB/app.js byId(audioTableWrap)?.addEventListener(click, ...)" as FE
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/WEB/app.js const api = async (url, options)" as APIJS
participant "TravelGuide.AdminWeb/Program.cs MapPut(/api/pois/{id})" as PUT
O -> RENDER : dataset.tab == audioTab -> renderAudioSources()
RENDER --> O : bảng audioUrl / mapLink từ mảng pois[]
O -> FE : Lưu từng dòng (handler trong app.js)
FE -> APIJS : await api(`/api/pois/${id}`, { method: PUT, body: JSON.stringify({ ... audioUrl, mapLink ... }) })
APIJS -> PUT : MapPut handler
FE -> FE : await loadPois(); renderAudioSources()
@enduml
